@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_flennq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.90)))
    tmp = wp.sin(0.27)
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.42)))
    v0 = (0.72 - ((v0 + 0.71 - tmp + 0.35) * (v1 + 0.02 - v0 + 0.61)))
    v0 = v2
    tmp = (0.12 - wp.sin((v0 + 0.41 - v2 + 0.21)))
    v1 = 0.76
    data[tid] = v0
